The paper discusses the improvement of Top-N recommendation systems, which is a common topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of convex and non-convex relaxations is also mentioned, which is a common technique in optimization (cs.DS) and statistics (cs.SI). Finally, the paper proposes a novel rank approximation, which is a technique commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
